// Team Dashboard
// Shows team-wide onboarding progress. Displays individual member completion cards,
// per-category coverage table, and a topic completion heatmap.

FUNCTION TeamDashboard()                                                EXPORT
  CALLS: getTeam (onboarding-api), getTopics (onboarding-api), getCategories (onboarding-api)
  Read project, currentUser from OnboardingContext.
  On mount: fetch team members, topics, and categories in parallel.
  Compute categoryCoverage: for each category, how many members have explored all its topics.
  Render:
    - Member cards showing each person's name, explored/total count, progress bar,
      and a "(you)" label for the current user.
    - Category coverage table with topic count and members-complete/total ratio.
    - Topic heatmap list: each topic with a color-coded dot (green=all explored, yellow=some, gray=none)
      and a ratio label, linking to the topic detail page.
